<details>
    <summary>Building Info</summary>

    <li>Here you can specify the amount of turns you'd like to invest into building different building types.</li> 
    <li>You initially build 1 building per turn.</li>
    <li>You can have up to 10 buildings per square mile of land.</li>
    <li>You can have up to 1 infrastructure per 1 square mile of land.</li>
</details>

<details>
    <summary>Demolish Info</summary>

    <li>You can demolish at 10 times your build rate</li> 
</details>

<br><b>Turns:</b> <%=@country.turns%>
<h4>Build: </h4><br>

<%= form_with url: user_game_path(@user_game), method: :patch, local: true do |form| %>

<details>
  <summary><b>Houses (<%=@country.houses%>)</b></summary>

  <li>Houses hold up to 1,000 population each</li>
  <li>Houses have an upkeep of $500 per turn</li>
  <li>Each citizen produces $25 a turn and has an upkeep of $15</li>
</details>

    <%= form.label :turns_to_build_houses %>
    <%= form.number_field :houses %> <br>

 <br><details>
  <summary><b>infrastructure (<%=@country.infrastructure%>)</b></summary>

  <li>infrastructure has an income of $1,500 per turn</li>
  <li>infrastructure has a base upkeep of $2,000 per turn and will become exponentially more expensive</li>
  <li>You build 1 additional building per turn for every 1,000 infrastructure. (IE 3 buildings per turn at 2000 infra)</li>
</details>

   <%= form.label :turns_to_build_infrastructure %>
    <%= form.number_field :infrastructure %> <br>

<br><details>
  <summary><b>Shops (<%=@country.shops%>)</b></summary>

  <li>Shops have an income of $15,000 per turn and expense of $5,000</li>
</details>

    <%= form.label :turns_to_build_shops %>
    <%= form.number_field :shops %><br>

<br><details>
  <summary><b>Barracks (<%=@country.barracks%>)</b></summary>

  <li>Each barracks increase maximum infantry by 150</li>
  <li>Barracks have an upkeep of $500 per turn</li>
</details>

    <%= form.label :turns_to_build_barracks %>
    <%= form.number_field :barracks %><br>

<br><details>
  <summary><b>Armories (<%=@country.armory%>)</b></summary>

  <li>Each armory increase maximum vehicles by 50 (25 for tanks)</li>
  <li>Arnmories have an upkeep of $500 per turn</li>
</details>

    <%= form.label :turns_to_build_armories %>
    <%= form.number_field :armories %><br>

<br><details>
  <summary><b>Hangars (<%=@country.hangars%>)</b></summary>

  <li>Each hangar increase maximum amount of aircraft. (multi-role fighters by 15, jet fighters by 10, naval bombers by 8, and heavy bombers by 5)</li>
  <li>Hangars have upkeep of $1,000 per turn</li>
</details>

    <%= form.label :turns_to_build_hangars %>
    <%= form.number_field :hangars %><br>

<br><details>
  <summary><b>Dockyards (<%=@country.dockyards%>)</b></summary>

  <li>Each dockyard increase maximum amount of ships. (corvettes by 10, frigates by 5, destroyers by 3, and cruisers by 2)</li>
  <li>Dockyards have upkeep of $2,500 per turn</li>
</details>

    <%= form.label :turns_to_build_dockyards %>
    <%= form.number_field :dockyards %><br>

<br><details>
  <summary><b>Labs (<%=@country.labs%>)</b></summary>

  <li>Each lab produces on research point per turn.</li>
  <li>Labs have upkeep of $10,000 per turn</li>
</details>

    <%= form.label :turns_to_build_labs %>
    <%= form.number_field :labs %><br>
  <%= form.submit "Build" %>
<% end %><br>

<h4>Demolish: </h4><br>

<%= form_with url: user_game_path(@user_game), method: :patch, local: true do |form| %>
    <%= form.label :turns_to_demolish_houses %>
    <%= form.number_field :demolish_houses %> <br>
    <%= form.label :turns_to_demolish_infrastructure %>
    <%= form.number_field :demolish_infrastructure %> <br>
    <%= form.label :turns_to_demolish_shops %>
    <%= form.number_field :demolish_shops %><br>
